WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 12=

00:01:43.650 --> 00:01:44.490 line:80%
Young Master,

00:01:46.370 --> 00:01:47.780 line:80%
Xing has nothing to do with this.

00:01:48.460 --> 00:01:50.730 line:80%
I am a despicable man without family.

00:01:51.180 --> 00:01:52.730 line:80%
But Xing is a good girl.

00:01:53.490 --> 00:01:54.330 line:80%
She once saved me

00:01:56.090 --> 00:01:57.900 line:80%
with a single bowl of rice.

00:01:58.700 --> 00:02:00.120 line:80%
They captured Xing.

00:02:00.500 --> 00:02:01.580 line:80%
I had no choice but...

00:02:04.180 --> 00:02:05.020 line:80%
Young Master,

00:02:06.700 --> 00:02:07.740 line:80%
my death means nothing.

00:02:08.780 --> 00:02:09.820 line:80%
I only have one request.

00:02:11.500 --> 00:02:12.860 line:80%
Please save Xing.

00:02:15.300 --> 00:02:16.300 line:80%
Who said I'd kill you?

00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:20.620 line:80%
You won't?

00:02:21.060 --> 00:02:23.460 line:80%
When you were 7,
you were sold into the Li Sect.

00:02:24.380 --> 00:02:25.900 line:80%
Elder Qiu saw your talent

00:02:26.260 --> 00:02:27.140 line:80%
and adopted you.

00:02:27.660 --> 00:02:29.033 line:80%
Later, because you handled affairs

00:02:29.044 --> 00:02:29.884 line:80%
with sharpness

00:02:30.100 --> 00:02:30.940 line:80%
and efficiency,

00:02:31.180 --> 00:02:32.300 line:80%
you earned Nie Zhe's trust

00:02:32.700 --> 00:02:34.273 line:80%
and became the Master of Qinglong Altar.

00:02:34.820 --> 00:02:35.660 line:80%
Later,

00:02:36.180 --> 00:02:37.553 line:80%
you fell out of favor with Nie Zhe.

00:02:37.940 --> 00:02:39.620 line:80%
But it was not because of incompetence.

00:02:39.980 --> 00:02:41.260 line:80%
It was because you had the altar

00:02:41.740 --> 00:02:42.860 line:80%
avoid taxes when you could

00:02:43.220 --> 00:02:44.420 line:80%
and delayed corvée labor

00:02:45.140 --> 00:02:46.060 line:80%
whenever possible.

00:02:47.340 --> 00:02:48.460 line:80%
After all these years,

00:02:49.100 --> 00:02:50.500 line:80%
the disciples under you benefited,

00:02:51.380 --> 00:02:52.220 line:80%
but Nie Zhe

00:02:52.740 --> 00:02:54.140 line:80%
gradually lost trust in you.

00:02:55.020 --> 00:02:55.860 line:80%
Young Master.

00:02:56.860 --> 00:02:58.220 line:80%
Someone once told me

00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:02.020 line:80%
that to judge a person,

00:03:03.140 --> 00:03:05.386 line:80%
you should not look at how good
they are in good times,

00:03:05.900 --> 00:03:08.100 line:80%
but how bad they can be in bad times.

00:03:09.180 --> 00:03:10.446 line:80%
You have fallen again and again.

00:03:11.860 --> 00:03:13.166 line:80%
You seem to drift with the wind,

00:03:13.580 --> 00:03:14.940 line:80%
yet you always act with restraint.

00:03:16.860 --> 00:03:17.700 line:80%
Therefore,

00:03:19.100 --> 00:03:20.260 line:80%
I am willing to keep you.

00:03:25.580 --> 00:03:26.820 line:80%
Young Master,

00:03:27.300 --> 00:03:28.580 line:80%
please bring Xing back.

00:03:30.060 --> 00:03:30.900 line:80%
I'll do

00:03:31.380 --> 00:03:32.460 line:80%
anything for you

00:03:33.220 --> 00:03:34.540 line:80%
and repay you with my life.

00:03:35.180 --> 00:03:36.386 line:80%
Return to Qinglong Altar first.

00:03:37.420 --> 00:03:38.260 line:80%
Wait for news.

00:03:41.500 --> 00:03:42.340 line:80%
Yes.

00:04:13.860 --> 00:04:15.260 line:80%
After the Six Sects were attacked,

00:04:15.347 --> 00:04:17.160 line:80%
many scouts were placed
along the post roads.

00:04:17.300 --> 00:04:18.420 line:80%
To avoid exposing our trail,

00:04:18.740 --> 00:04:19.840 line:80%
we must disguise ourselves.

00:04:20.380 --> 00:04:21.366 line:80%
There are clothes inside.

00:04:21.700 --> 00:04:23.500 line:80%
You're so thoughtful.

00:04:28.140 --> 00:04:29.780 line:80%
You're truly diligent and studious.

00:04:29.980 --> 00:04:31.340 line:80%
You even bring books on a trip.

00:04:32.300 --> 00:04:35.420 line:80%
100 Ways to Win a Lady Over?

00:04:40.180 --> 00:04:41.460 line:80%
(100 Ways)
Yuzhi is slow-witted.

00:04:41.540 --> 00:04:42.500 line:80%
I have to worry more.

00:04:55.300 --> 00:04:56.300 line:80%
I believe

00:04:56.500 --> 00:04:58.820 line:80%
Lingbo will surely understand

00:04:58.940 --> 00:05:00.380 line:80%
your feelings for her.

00:05:02.739 --> 00:05:03.878 line:80%
I'll go change clothes first.

00:05:12.580 --> 00:05:14.260 line:80%
(100 Ways to Win a Lady Over)

00:05:29.340 --> 00:05:30.786 line:80%
(Shangguan Haonan)
What do you mean?

00:05:30.940 --> 00:05:32.060 line:80%
Are you trying to rebel?

00:05:36.460 --> 00:05:37.300 line:80%
Chief.

00:05:42.060 --> 00:05:43.020 line:80%
What happened.

00:05:43.660 --> 00:05:44.309 line:80%
Chief,

00:05:44.320 --> 00:05:46.020 line:80%
today's assassination attempt
on Mu Qingyan

00:05:46.020 --> 00:05:47.493 line:80%
was stopped by a group of masked men.

00:05:47.540 --> 00:05:48.700 line:80%
The leader's build

00:05:49.060 --> 00:05:49.900 line:80%
and moves

00:05:50.533 --> 00:05:51.719 line:80%
closely resembled Shangguan's.

00:05:53.260 --> 00:05:54.500 line:80%
Within the sect,

00:05:54.820 --> 00:05:55.900 line:80%
only he can fight me

00:05:55.900 --> 00:05:57.140 line:80%
and gather so many men

00:05:57.660 --> 00:05:58.500 line:80%
in just a few days.

00:05:59.740 --> 00:06:00.580 line:80%
Chief...

00:06:12.540 --> 00:06:13.380 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:06:13.620 --> 00:06:14.460 line:80%
what do you say?

00:06:14.820 --> 00:06:16.260 line:80%
She's just framing me.

00:06:17.313 --> 00:06:18.620 line:80%
You failed in the assassination

00:06:18.620 --> 00:06:19.913 line:80%
and want me to take the blame.

00:06:20.100 --> 00:06:21.620 line:80%
So, please produce some solid evidence.

00:06:22.300 --> 00:06:23.500 line:80%
What builds and moves?

00:06:24.900 --> 00:06:26.020 line:80%
That is sheer nonsense.

00:06:26.399 --> 00:06:27.792 line:80%
The sect is full of hidden talents.

00:06:28.180 --> 00:06:29.406 line:80%
The Mu clan is deeply rooted.

00:06:29.820 --> 00:06:31.300 line:80%
What is strange about Mu Qingyan

00:06:31.353 --> 00:06:32.413 line:80%
having experts by his side?

00:06:32.740 --> 00:06:33.706 line:80%
At the Chen hour today,

00:06:34.540 --> 00:06:35.740 line:80%
Mr. Shangguan, where are you?

00:06:36.500 --> 00:06:37.700 line:80%
And who can testify for you?

00:06:39.500 --> 00:06:40.420 line:80%
You can't answer that?

00:06:40.820 --> 00:06:41.880 line:80%
Clearly, you're suspicious.

00:06:41.980 --> 00:06:44.580 line:80%
This morning, Shangguan was with me.

00:06:48.140 --> 00:06:48.980 line:80%
Elder Hu,

00:06:49.900 --> 00:06:51.340 line:80%
since the Chief has testified,

00:06:51.820 --> 00:06:54.060 line:80%
Shangguan is naturally innocent.

00:06:55.540 --> 00:06:57.260 line:80%
Do not bring this up again.

00:07:00.460 --> 00:07:01.720 line:80%
It's my fault for being careless

00:07:02.660 --> 00:07:04.540 line:80%
and failing to capture Chang Ning.

00:07:08.980 --> 00:07:10.520 line:80%
It's only right that people suspect me.

00:07:12.420 --> 00:07:14.100 line:80%
I request to go to Xuanwu Altar

00:07:14.380 --> 00:07:15.860 line:80%
and intercept Mu Qingyan.

00:07:16.220 --> 00:07:17.420 line:80%
What are you going there for?

00:07:18.180 --> 00:07:19.500 line:80%
No one is blaming you.

00:07:19.500 --> 00:07:21.340 line:80%
A real man shoulders responsibility.

00:07:22.220 --> 00:07:23.780 line:80%
Mu Qingyan has taken over Qinglong Altar

00:07:24.033 --> 00:07:25.920 line:80%
and will surely set his sights
on Xuanwu Altar.

00:07:25.940 --> 00:07:27.860 line:80%
I am no coward who clings to life.

00:07:28.420 --> 00:07:29.300 line:80%
Chief, please allow me

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:30.480 line:80%
to guard the altar.

00:07:42.006 --> 00:07:42.995 line:80%
Shangguan acts in secret.

00:07:43.006 --> 00:07:44.100 line:80%
He must be hiding something.

00:07:44.100 --> 00:07:46.700 line:80%
Xiong Qianjin of Xuanwu Altar is my man.

00:07:47.180 --> 00:07:48.900 line:80%
I will order him to watch Shangguan

00:07:49.180 --> 00:07:50.193 line:80%
and kill him if there is

00:07:50.460 --> 00:07:51.460 line:80%
any unusual movement.

00:07:51.460 --> 00:07:53.340 line:80%
But the Chief is
quite fond of Shangguan.

00:07:53.860 --> 00:07:55.380 line:80%
If he investigates...

00:07:55.620 --> 00:07:56.780 line:80%
We'll say

00:07:57.420 --> 00:07:59.820 line:80%
Mu Qingyan killed Shangguan.

00:08:37.313 --> 00:08:39.066 line:80%
We're already
in the demon sect's territory.

00:08:39.180 --> 00:08:40.260 line:80%
There are Six Sects scouts

00:08:40.260 --> 00:08:41.380 line:80%
and demon sect spies.

00:08:41.940 --> 00:08:42.820 line:80%
The situation

00:08:42.820 --> 00:08:43.740 line:80%
is very complicated.

00:08:44.460 --> 00:08:46.900 line:80%
A gentleman does not stand
beneath a crumbling wall.

00:08:47.100 --> 00:08:48.140 line:80%
We must be very cautious.

00:08:48.660 --> 00:08:49.500 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:08:49.900 --> 00:08:51.980 line:80%
you're saying with a lot of energy.

00:08:52.620 --> 00:08:53.940 line:80%
The moon is also beautiful.

00:08:54.300 --> 00:08:55.980 line:80%
Why don't we continue on our way?

00:08:57.940 --> 00:08:59.380 line:80%
Mr. Mu is indeed in danger,

00:08:59.900 --> 00:09:00.889 line:80%
but with his capability,

00:09:00.900 --> 00:09:01.913 line:80%
his life is not at risk.

00:09:02.620 --> 00:09:03.893 line:80%
There is no need for us to rush.

00:09:04.500 --> 00:09:06.020 line:80%
Are you eager to see him?

00:09:08.380 --> 00:09:10.380 line:80%
You keep talking about gentlemen.

00:09:10.660 --> 00:09:11.629 line:80%
A gentleman should repay

00:09:11.640 --> 00:09:12.940 line:80%
a peach for a plum

00:09:12.940 --> 00:09:13.900 line:80%
or jade for wood, right?

00:09:18.500 --> 00:09:19.660 line:80%
You're in such a hurry.

00:09:20.060 --> 00:09:20.900 line:80%
Does he know?

00:09:28.260 --> 00:09:29.820 line:80%
Is Zhao really coming to help me?

00:09:30.780 --> 00:09:31.660 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:09:31.940 --> 00:09:33.460 line:80%
I did not fail the task

00:09:33.860 --> 00:09:36.300 line:80%
and have stopped Miss Cai.

00:09:39.220 --> 00:09:40.320 line:80%
If she truly wanted to come,

00:09:40.920 --> 00:09:42.193 line:80%
how could you possibly stop her?

00:09:42.940 --> 00:09:44.180 line:80%
Are you saying

00:09:44.860 --> 00:09:46.260 line:80%
Miss Cai is already here?

00:09:54.900 --> 00:09:55.740 line:80%
Go find her.

00:10:07.820 --> 00:10:09.100 line:80%
Ahead lie the Hanhai Mountains.

00:10:16.300 --> 00:10:17.180 line:80%
Do you smell anything?

00:10:18.060 --> 00:10:18.900 line:80%
What?

00:10:22.220 --> 00:10:23.220 line:80%
Roasted buns.

00:10:25.380 --> 00:10:26.580 line:80%
And pancakes and wonton.

00:10:29.500 --> 00:10:30.660 line:80%
This one is a bit small.

00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:32.620 line:80%
I want the big one.

00:10:32.620 --> 00:10:33.940 line:80%
Sure. I will wrap them for you.

00:10:34.700 --> 00:10:35.700 line:80%
Bracelets at a low price!

00:10:38.140 --> 00:10:39.140 line:80%
Fresh mandarins!

00:10:40.220 --> 00:10:42.700 line:80%
Waterproof rain cloaks!

00:10:42.700 --> 00:10:45.140 line:80%
It often rains! It's a must!

00:10:46.140 --> 00:10:48.300 line:80%
Everyone avoids the demon.

00:10:48.700 --> 00:10:49.933 line:80%
How can there be a market here?

00:10:50.140 --> 00:10:51.180 line:80%
You do not understand.

00:10:51.980 --> 00:10:53.633 line:80%
This is called seeking fortune
in danger.

00:10:54.380 --> 00:10:55.220 line:80%
Setting up a stall

00:10:55.380 --> 00:10:56.500 line:80%
is for making money.

00:10:57.060 --> 00:10:58.780 line:80%
Where there are people, there is trade.

00:10:59.460 --> 00:11:01.020 line:80%
The elite of the Six Sects are all out,

00:11:01.220 --> 00:11:03.220 line:80%
gathering nearby for information,

00:11:03.290 --> 00:11:04.140 line:80%
so this must be

00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:06.300 line:80%
the liveliest place
in the entire Jianghu.

00:11:06.740 --> 00:11:07.580 line:80%
Another day,

00:11:07.780 --> 00:11:09.473 line:80%
I will have the uncles
from Luoying Valley

00:11:09.484 --> 00:11:10.420 line:80%
come and see

00:11:10.700 --> 00:11:12.140 line:80%
how they do business.

00:11:13.740 --> 00:11:14.980 line:80%
Instead of studying business,

00:11:15.700 --> 00:11:16.860 line:80%
we should first think of a way

00:11:16.860 --> 00:11:18.206 line:80%
to find the demon sect's entrance.

00:11:20.780 --> 00:11:21.699 line:80%
The Li Sect's entrance.

00:11:23.220 --> 00:11:24.660 line:80%
I can take you there.

00:11:25.820 --> 00:11:27.420 line:80%
(Xue Youfu)

00:11:38.380 --> 00:11:39.220 line:80%
Sir,

00:11:39.380 --> 00:11:40.860 line:80%
you are not from the Li Sect,

00:11:40.860 --> 00:11:42.146 line:80%
so how do you know the entrance?

00:11:42.620 --> 00:11:44.260 line:80%
People of the Li Sect are still people.

00:11:44.540 --> 00:11:45.900 line:80%
They need to live a life

00:11:46.180 --> 00:11:47.540 line:80%
and buy hairpins and cloth.

00:11:47.740 --> 00:11:49.220 line:80%
I just happened to help them

00:11:49.220 --> 00:11:51.460 line:80%
transport goods once by accident.

00:11:51.460 --> 00:11:54.060 line:80%
After one time,
there were countless more.

00:11:54.260 --> 00:11:55.660 line:80%
This is how business works.

00:11:55.893 --> 00:11:57.262 line:80%
You have both courage and insight.

00:11:57.340 --> 00:11:58.353 line:80%
Your future is boundless.

00:12:00.340 --> 00:12:01.260 line:80%
Sir,

00:12:01.260 --> 00:12:02.860 line:80%
what does the Li Sect look like inside?

00:12:02.900 --> 00:12:04.780 line:80%
I never saw their members.

00:12:05.180 --> 00:12:06.940 line:80%
I mostly deal with nearby villagers

00:12:07.140 --> 00:12:08.340 line:80%
and hunters.

00:12:08.700 --> 00:12:09.540 line:80%
But I have heard

00:12:10.580 --> 00:12:12.500 line:80%
the Li Sect is full of traps.

00:12:12.660 --> 00:12:14.900 line:80%
The only passage open to the outside

00:12:14.939 --> 00:12:16.540 line:80%
is layered with mechanisms and arrows.

00:12:16.540 --> 00:12:18.253 line:80%
People of Jianghu call it
the Youming Path.

00:12:18.264 --> 00:12:20.220 line:80%
It is a place of no return.

00:12:22.060 --> 00:12:22.900 line:80%
The price

00:12:23.380 --> 00:12:24.300 line:80%
must be doubled.

00:12:25.860 --> 00:12:26.700 line:80%
Why?

00:12:26.900 --> 00:12:28.220 line:80%
Because there are two of you.

00:12:34.420 --> 00:12:35.380 line:80%
Taking advantage of us?

00:12:37.740 --> 00:12:38.780 line:80%
Reasonable and justified.

00:12:39.220 --> 00:12:40.580 line:80%
You do have a talent for business.

00:12:43.820 --> 00:12:45.460 line:80%
Well, in business...

00:12:48.300 --> 00:12:49.140 line:80%
Miss,

00:12:50.340 --> 00:12:51.900 line:80%
have you lost your mind?

00:12:51.900 --> 00:12:53.500 line:80%
I'm extorting you.

00:12:53.500 --> 00:12:55.153 line:80%
Let me be clear.
Whatever tricks you try,

00:12:55.164 --> 00:12:56.324 line:80%
this money must be paid.

00:12:57.660 --> 00:12:58.500 line:80%
Thank you.

00:13:00.660 --> 00:13:01.500 line:80%
You are

00:13:01.980 --> 00:13:02.820 line:80%
so considerate?

00:13:04.100 --> 00:13:05.260 line:80%
If not making a living,

00:13:05.500 --> 00:13:07.293 line:80%
who'd choose to scrape by
around the Li Sect?

00:13:08.060 --> 00:13:08.900 line:80%
Take it.

00:13:10.340 --> 00:13:11.180 line:80%
You two

00:13:13.580 --> 00:13:14.420 line:80%
are simply

00:13:16.100 --> 00:13:16.940 line:80%
too foolish.

00:13:18.260 --> 00:13:19.100 line:80%
Sit tight.

00:13:26.540 --> 00:13:27.380 line:80%
Sir?

00:13:35.580 --> 00:13:36.780 line:80%
I even praised him just now.

00:13:37.433 --> 00:13:38.782 line:80%
Taking money without doing the job.

00:13:38.860 --> 00:13:39.806 line:80%
He's not honest at all.

00:13:40.140 --> 00:13:40.980 line:80%
Zhao,

00:13:41.140 --> 00:13:41.980 line:80%
what should we do?

00:13:54.940 --> 00:13:55.780 line:80%
Xiaolan.

00:14:00.540 --> 00:14:01.660 line:80%
What do you need?

00:14:01.940 --> 00:14:03.400 line:80%
It's been days since I last saw Zhao.

00:14:03.740 --> 00:14:04.580 line:80%
Is something wrong?

00:14:05.660 --> 00:14:06.580 line:80%
Nothing.

00:14:06.580 --> 00:14:07.420 line:80%
Everything is fine.

00:14:14.340 --> 00:14:15.180 line:80%
I do not believe it.

00:14:16.260 --> 00:14:17.700 line:80%
Zhao...

00:14:18.100 --> 00:14:18.940 line:80%
She...

00:14:20.900 --> 00:14:22.140 line:80%
She has chickenpox.

00:14:24.540 --> 00:14:26.180 line:80%
Has Uncle Lei prescribed medicine?

00:14:27.660 --> 00:14:28.660 line:80%
Do not worry.

00:14:28.660 --> 00:14:29.900 line:80%
Feicui is looking after her.

00:14:30.140 --> 00:14:31.020 line:80%
Zhao is fine.

00:14:33.300 --> 00:14:34.700 line:80%
Zhao has chickenpox.

00:14:35.540 --> 00:14:36.620 line:80%
Yuzhi has caught a chill.

00:14:37.340 --> 00:14:38.260 line:80%
Well...

00:14:38.260 --> 00:14:39.100 line:80%
Master.

00:14:40.060 --> 00:14:40.900 line:80%
Master.

00:14:41.700 --> 00:14:42.540 line:80%
- Master.
- Master.

00:14:43.300 --> 00:14:44.140 line:80%
Master.

00:14:51.300 --> 00:14:52.180 line:80%
Keep practicing.

00:14:52.180 --> 00:14:53.020 line:80%
Yes.

00:14:56.380 --> 00:14:58.460 line:80%
(To Master, From Yuzhi)

00:14:58.620 --> 00:15:00.460 line:80%
Yuzhi wishes to go out
to clear his mind.

00:15:01.140 --> 00:15:02.660 line:80%
Why did he not tell me in person?

00:15:03.620 --> 00:15:05.980 line:80%
You were about to enter seclusion.

00:15:06.740 --> 00:15:07.700 line:80%
He feared troubling you,

00:15:07.967 --> 00:15:09.067 line:80%
so he left a letter instead.

00:15:09.580 --> 00:15:10.420 line:80%
Where did he go?

00:15:11.820 --> 00:15:13.620 line:80%
Guangtian Gate governs a vast territory.

00:15:13.940 --> 00:15:14.800 line:80%
Lord Song

00:15:14.810 --> 00:15:16.940 line:80%
has long hoped he'd travel more.

00:15:17.340 --> 00:15:19.540 line:80%
So, he went to inspect the territories.

00:15:20.340 --> 00:15:22.420 line:80%
He also asked me to tell you:

00:15:24.100 --> 00:15:25.860 line:80%
His remaining 50% strength

00:15:26.220 --> 00:15:27.580 line:80%
is enough to deal with punks,

00:15:27.980 --> 00:15:28.980 line:80%
so you needn't worry.

00:15:30.940 --> 00:15:32.580 line:80%
Since he's inspecting territories,

00:15:33.940 --> 00:15:35.820 line:80%
why would he need to deal with punks?

00:15:47.100 --> 00:15:47.940 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:15:48.820 --> 00:15:49.660 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:15:49.900 --> 00:15:50.780 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:15:50.780 --> 00:15:51.820 line:80%
You can't die.

00:15:53.100 --> 00:15:53.980 line:80%
If you die,

00:15:53.980 --> 00:15:55.473 line:80%
how am I supposed to face your father?

00:15:55.740 --> 00:15:57.060 line:80%
Wake up, Yuzhi.

00:15:57.820 --> 00:15:58.660 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:15:58.860 --> 00:15:59.820 line:80%
Wake up.

00:16:03.660 --> 00:16:04.540 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:16:06.300 --> 00:16:07.140 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:16:20.140 --> 00:16:22.020 line:80%
I wonder whether Zhao
has found Chang Ning.

00:16:23.620 --> 00:16:24.460 line:80%
Chickenpox

00:16:25.180 --> 00:16:26.020 line:80%
is contagious.

00:16:27.060 --> 00:16:28.140 line:80%
She can't go out.

00:16:32.020 --> 00:16:33.780 line:80%
Master.

00:16:34.180 --> 00:16:35.020 line:80%
Why is Zhao ill?

00:16:35.220 --> 00:16:36.300 line:80%
Chickenpox is contagious.

00:16:36.460 --> 00:16:37.540 line:80%
Then why are you here?

00:16:39.900 --> 00:16:41.620 line:80%
I was worried about Zhao,

00:16:42.060 --> 00:16:43.046 line:80%
so I came to take a look.

00:16:44.940 --> 00:16:46.460 line:80%
Master,

00:16:46.460 --> 00:16:47.780 line:80%
chickenpox is contagious.

00:16:47.939 --> 00:16:49.268 line:80%
Why not wait until Zhao recovers?

00:16:49.279 --> 00:16:50.559 line:80%
Then I will have her go see you.

00:16:58.100 --> 00:16:59.220 line:80%
Zhao is usually someone

00:16:59.220 --> 00:17:01.180 line:80%
who sits and lies down

00:17:01.180 --> 00:17:02.420 line:80%
whenever she can.

00:17:02.780 --> 00:17:04.340 line:80%
When has she ever sat so straight?

00:17:05.020 --> 00:17:05.860 line:80%
Also,

00:17:06.820 --> 00:17:08.980 line:80%
she's holding Eighteen Years Waiting.

00:17:09.420 --> 00:17:11.180 line:80%
She hates it the most,

00:17:11.500 --> 00:17:13.380 line:80%
saying Li Baochuan
is foolish and stupid.

00:17:13.620 --> 00:17:15.020 line:80%
How could she be so absorbed in it?

00:17:17.660 --> 00:17:18.500 line:80%
Feicui.

00:17:23.500 --> 00:17:24.380 line:80%
Tell me.

00:17:24.380 --> 00:17:25.220 line:80%
Where are Zhao

00:17:25.540 --> 00:17:26.660 line:80%
and Yuzhi now?

00:17:27.180 --> 00:17:31.820 line:80%
(Hanhai Nightmares)

00:17:59.526 --> 00:18:00.832 line:80%
Abnormality is demonic in nature.

00:18:01.060 --> 00:18:02.740 line:80%
Do not let anything approach.

00:18:50.660 --> 00:18:52.300 line:80%
Manager Cai.

00:18:53.700 --> 00:18:55.260 line:80%
Manager Zhao?

00:19:08.860 --> 00:19:09.780 line:80%
Manager Zhao.

00:19:11.500 --> 00:19:12.700 line:80%
(Cold Moon Blade)

00:19:12.940 --> 00:19:13.940 line:80%
Manager.

00:19:16.340 --> 00:19:17.860 line:80%
Qingyan, what is it?

00:19:18.420 --> 00:19:20.740 line:80%
Following your brilliant strategies,

00:19:20.940 --> 00:19:22.560 line:80%
we've worked hard and refined ourselves,

00:19:22.620 --> 00:19:24.020 line:80%
and truly turned Luoying Town

00:19:24.020 --> 00:19:26.580 line:80%
into the most prosperous market
in the neighborhood.

00:19:28.780 --> 00:19:29.620 line:80%
Good.

00:19:29.620 --> 00:19:30.580 line:80%
Very good.

00:19:30.900 --> 00:19:31.740 line:80%
The ledger.

00:19:36.740 --> 00:19:37.740 line:80%
Here. Open your mouth.

00:19:41.780 --> 00:19:42.620 line:80%
Lately,

00:19:42.780 --> 00:19:43.933 line:80%
you've grown more perceptive.

00:19:45.860 --> 00:19:47.700 line:80%
You saved my life

00:19:48.180 --> 00:19:49.580 line:80%
and even took me in as a follower.

00:19:49.780 --> 00:19:51.900 line:80%
To repay such kindness,

00:19:52.260 --> 00:19:55.460 line:80%
I can only try my best to serve you.

00:19:55.530 --> 00:19:56.380 line:80%
From now on,

00:19:56.380 --> 00:19:58.020 line:80%
you will follow me.

00:19:58.020 --> 00:20:00.100 line:80%
You'll surely have an amazing life.

00:20:00.620 --> 00:20:02.140 line:80%
Thank you, Manager Cai.

00:21:18.860 --> 00:21:20.380 line:80%
Yuzhi has gone mad?

00:21:21.660 --> 00:21:22.500 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:21:23.380 --> 00:21:24.420 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:21:25.940 --> 00:21:26.780 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:21:27.180 --> 00:21:28.020 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:21:32.620 --> 00:21:33.460 line:80%
You slapped me again?

00:21:34.180 --> 00:21:35.020 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:21:35.420 --> 00:21:36.540 line:80%
I couldn't wake you up.

00:21:36.900 --> 00:21:37.900 line:80%
What did you dream about?

00:21:38.620 --> 00:21:39.460 line:80%
I...

00:21:39.780 --> 00:21:42.020 line:80%
I dreamed that I became a butterfly
and flew away.

00:21:42.020 --> 00:21:42.860 line:80%
Me, too.

00:21:46.333 --> 00:21:47.593 line:80%
These butterflies are poisonous.

00:21:48.860 --> 00:21:50.100 line:80%
It seems we were both affected.

00:22:03.140 --> 00:22:04.460 line:80%
I think my aunt once told me

00:22:04.471 --> 00:22:06.089 line:80%
this is called the Nightmare Butterfly.

00:22:06.100 --> 00:22:07.940 line:80%
It was born from Zhuang Zhou's dream.

00:22:08.500 --> 00:22:09.380 line:80%
It feeds in dreams,

00:22:09.533 --> 00:22:10.966 line:80%
more dangerous than the Guming Moth.

00:22:11.111 --> 00:22:13.446 line:80%
It must've been Uncle Cheng's amulet
that saved our lives.

00:22:13.540 --> 00:22:15.353 line:80%
Otherwise, we would've died
in the nightmare.

00:22:15.780 --> 00:22:17.100 line:80%
The demon sect is full of tricks.

00:22:27.140 --> 00:22:27.980 line:80%
Run!

00:22:45.820 --> 00:22:46.660 line:80%
Lord Song,

00:22:47.088 --> 00:22:48.008 line:80%
if we travel like this,

00:22:48.019 --> 00:22:50.569 line:80%
it'll take at least half a month
to reach the Hanhai Mountains.

00:22:50.580 --> 00:22:51.769 line:80%
Why not switch to fast horses?

00:22:51.780 --> 00:22:53.460 line:80%
Why the rush?

00:22:54.340 --> 00:22:57.500 line:80%
It's not a bad thing for young people
to experience the world.

00:22:58.413 --> 00:23:00.179 line:80%
But Mr. Song is heading
into the demon sect.

00:23:01.580 --> 00:23:02.653 line:80%
This time, my son managed

00:23:02.664 --> 00:23:05.060 line:80%
to secretly take Zhao away.

00:23:05.420 --> 00:23:07.300 line:80%
That brings glory to our Guangtian Gate.

00:23:07.900 --> 00:23:08.826 line:80%
As for where they went,

00:23:08.966 --> 00:23:10.020 line:80%
it does not matter at all.

00:23:11.020 --> 00:23:11.940 line:80%
This time,

00:23:12.060 --> 00:23:14.780 line:80%
Yuzhi has really made me proud.

00:23:17.940 --> 00:23:19.780 line:80%
The 100 Ways to Win a Lady Over

00:23:19.780 --> 00:23:22.140 line:80%
that I gave him truly worked.

00:23:25.860 --> 00:23:26.700 line:80%
What is going on?

00:23:26.860 --> 00:23:28.100 line:80%
Lord Song, a pigeon message.

00:23:32.860 --> 00:23:36.220 line:80%
(Please join me to protect the kids.)

00:23:36.780 --> 00:23:37.620 line:80%
Lord Song,

00:23:38.180 --> 00:23:39.220 line:80%
Lord Qi has arrived.

00:23:44.940 --> 00:23:47.980 line:80%
(Toxins Abyss)

00:24:01.580 --> 00:24:02.860 line:80%
This place is filled with poison.

00:24:03.820 --> 00:24:04.660 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:24:04.859 --> 00:24:06.359 line:80%
you should protect yourself as well.

00:24:06.820 --> 00:24:07.660 line:80%
No.

00:24:35.180 --> 00:24:36.020 line:80%
Let's go.

00:25:10.420 --> 00:25:11.260 line:80%
Run!

00:25:53.660 --> 00:25:54.540 line:80%
Stop!

00:25:59.020 --> 00:26:00.460 line:80%
It is that heinous swindler.

00:26:03.700 --> 00:26:05.140 line:80%
The Demonic Camp.

00:26:05.733 --> 00:26:06.660 line:80%
I take the left three.

00:26:06.660 --> 00:26:07.619 line:80%
You take the right two.

00:27:08.970 --> 00:27:09.820 line:80%
Sir,

00:27:09.820 --> 00:27:11.740 line:80%
fortune turns in cycles.

00:27:18.420 --> 00:27:20.060 line:80%
I finally found you.

00:27:24.420 --> 00:27:26.420 line:80%
What happened to you two?

00:27:29.660 --> 00:27:31.060 line:80%
Let us first wash our faces

00:27:31.740 --> 00:27:32.580 line:80%
and have a meal.

00:27:34.860 --> 00:27:38.740 line:80%
(Li Sect's village, Peace and Plenty)

00:27:39.790 --> 00:27:40.660 line:80%
You're back?

00:27:40.660 --> 00:27:41.500 line:80%
Yeah.

00:27:42.700 --> 00:27:43.540 line:80%
Welcome back.

00:27:43.870 --> 00:27:44.740 line:80%
Welcome back.

00:27:44.740 --> 00:27:45.780 line:80%
- Ms. Li.
- Youfu is back.

00:27:48.060 --> 00:27:49.460 line:80%
So, the demon sect is like this.

00:27:49.780 --> 00:27:51.420 line:80%
- Uncle.
- Welcome back.

00:27:51.420 --> 00:27:52.846 line:80%
Perhaps, like the nightmare fields,

00:27:53.220 --> 00:27:54.620 line:80%
it looks picturesque on the surface

00:27:55.260 --> 00:27:56.820 line:80%
but hides deadly danger beneath.

00:27:56.820 --> 00:27:57.660 line:80%
I'm back.

00:27:58.380 --> 00:27:59.220 line:80%
Youfu, you're back.

00:27:59.220 --> 00:28:00.620 line:80%
- Yeah.
- Welcome back.

00:28:00.780 --> 00:28:01.620 line:80%
Uncle Xue!

00:28:02.740 --> 00:28:04.100 line:80%
- Uncle Xue.
- Uncle Xue.

00:28:04.340 --> 00:28:05.260 line:80%
Come on.

00:28:05.260 --> 00:28:06.100 line:80%
Hold out your hands.

00:28:06.170 --> 00:28:07.040 line:80%
Yours.

00:28:07.060 --> 00:28:08.670 line:80%
- And yours.
- Thanks.

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:09.600 line:80%
Yours.

00:28:09.610 --> 00:28:10.460 line:80%
- Thanks.
- Yours.

00:28:10.480 --> 00:28:11.900 line:80%
- Thanks.
- Go play.

00:28:28.300 --> 00:28:30.780 line:80%
Do not blame me.

00:28:31.140 --> 00:28:33.260 line:80%
The journey was too dangerous.

00:28:33.500 --> 00:28:35.540 line:80%
I could tell you two are good people,

00:28:35.780 --> 00:28:36.620 line:80%
so I deliberately

00:28:36.740 --> 00:28:38.340 line:80%
sent you back.

00:28:38.980 --> 00:28:39.820 line:80%
Does that mean

00:28:40.260 --> 00:28:41.420 line:80%
we should thank you instead?

00:28:41.420 --> 00:28:42.260 line:80%
No need.

00:28:42.700 --> 00:28:45.540 line:80%
Upholding justice is our duty.

00:28:49.340 --> 00:28:50.180 line:80%
Uncle Xue,

00:28:50.380 --> 00:28:51.380 line:80%
you're quite shameless.

00:28:51.780 --> 00:28:53.153 line:80%
You truly are cut out for business.

00:28:55.260 --> 00:28:56.740 line:80%
Where is my golden silk armor?

00:29:00.140 --> 00:29:02.220 line:80%
After we fell into the water,
you took our bundle.

00:29:03.500 --> 00:29:04.660 line:80%
Does it fit you well?

00:29:07.660 --> 00:29:08.586 line:80%
What golden silk armor?

00:29:11.653 --> 00:29:13.519 line:80%
You were hit by throwing darts
and did not die.

00:29:14.100 --> 00:29:16.340 line:80%
Was it not my golden silk armor
that blocked it for you?

00:29:18.620 --> 00:29:19.460 line:80%
However,

00:29:20.140 --> 00:29:21.900 line:80%
your sickle also saved my life.

00:29:22.180 --> 00:29:23.740 line:80%
Let us call it even.

00:29:24.020 --> 00:29:25.221 line:80%
I will not pursue the matter

00:29:25.232 --> 00:29:26.606 line:80%
of you abandoning us midway.

00:29:26.767 --> 00:29:28.596 line:80%
But that golden silk armor
is meant as a gift.

00:29:28.780 --> 00:29:29.700 line:80%
Return it now.

00:29:32.820 --> 00:29:34.100 line:80%
I also stewed chicken soup.

00:29:34.100 --> 00:29:34.940 line:80%
I will go bring it.

00:29:38.373 --> 00:29:39.340 line:80%
Is the golden silk armor

00:29:39.740 --> 00:29:40.900 line:80%
for Mr. Mu?

00:29:41.900 --> 00:29:43.460 line:80%
He once risked his life to save me.

00:29:44.386 --> 00:29:45.860 line:80%
This is my way of returning the favor.

00:29:48.620 --> 00:29:52.220 line:80%
(Qinglong Altar)

00:29:52.220 --> 00:29:53.620 line:80%
(Bliss Palace)

00:29:54.380 --> 00:29:55.220 line:80%
Young Master.

00:29:55.540 --> 00:29:56.406 line:80%
Father planned ahead

00:29:56.417 --> 00:29:58.626 line:80%
and ordered us to dig
several secret tunnels years ago.

00:29:59.053 --> 00:30:00.433 line:80%
If we leave through those tunnels,

00:30:01.020 --> 00:30:02.500 line:80%
we can avoid all checkpoints

00:30:02.706 --> 00:30:03.980 line:80%
and go straight to Bliss Palace.

00:30:03.980 --> 00:30:04.820 line:80%
(Bliss Palace)

00:30:08.660 --> 00:30:10.660 line:80%
(Xuanwu Altar)

00:30:10.813 --> 00:30:12.700 line:80%
But this time,
I want to take a different path.

00:30:14.180 --> 00:30:15.020 line:80%
Guanyue,

00:30:15.140 --> 00:30:16.580 line:80%
do you know

00:30:16.580 --> 00:30:18.100 line:80%
how to clean a filthy room?

00:30:19.820 --> 00:30:20.660 line:80%
How?

00:30:20.860 --> 00:30:21.700 line:80%
I once thought

00:30:22.020 --> 00:30:24.060 line:80%
that all it took was
to replace the owner.

00:30:24.860 --> 00:30:25.900 line:80%
But later, I realized

00:30:26.980 --> 00:30:29.580 line:80%
the room was not merely filthy.

00:30:29.900 --> 00:30:31.340 line:80%
Even the foundation and beams

00:30:32.140 --> 00:30:34.700 line:80%
have long been eaten away
by snakes and rats.

00:30:35.180 --> 00:30:37.100 line:80%
The best way to clean a room

00:30:37.740 --> 00:30:38.740 line:80%
is not to clean it,

00:30:40.260 --> 00:30:41.820 line:80%
but to burn it down with one fire

00:30:43.420 --> 00:30:44.340 line:80%
and rebuild it anew.

00:30:45.380 --> 00:30:46.780 line:80%
Are you saying...?

00:30:49.620 --> 00:30:51.300 line:80%
This time, I'll slaughter my way

00:30:52.020 --> 00:30:52.993 line:80%
through the Youming Path,

00:30:53.660 --> 00:30:54.500 line:80%
step by step,

00:30:55.980 --> 00:30:57.220 line:80%
to Bliss Palace.

00:30:58.220 --> 00:30:59.060 line:80%
We'll fight?

00:30:59.820 --> 00:31:00.780 line:80%
What about Xing?

00:31:00.980 --> 00:31:02.060 line:80%
Master You, rest assured.

00:31:03.260 --> 00:31:04.620 line:80%
Xing's whereabouts

00:31:05.940 --> 00:31:06.860 line:80%
have been found.

00:31:14.220 --> 00:31:15.060 line:80%
Here.

00:31:20.490 --> 00:31:21.340 line:80%
My...

00:31:21.340 --> 00:31:22.220 line:80%
Well.

00:31:22.420 --> 00:31:24.900 line:80%
How did you get
through the nightmare fields?

00:31:25.540 --> 00:31:26.860 line:80%
Since it appeared,

00:31:27.040 --> 00:31:29.073 line:80%
very few people have been able
to reach this place.

00:31:29.126 --> 00:31:30.849 line:80%
The nightmare fields
were not always there.

00:31:30.980 --> 00:31:32.173 line:80%
They appeared in recent years.

00:31:32.620 --> 00:31:33.460 line:80%
It was said to be

00:31:33.733 --> 00:31:35.540 line:80%
to prevent the Six Sects
from causing trouble.

00:31:36.340 --> 00:31:37.620 line:80%
I was lucky.

00:31:38.020 --> 00:31:39.300 line:80%
When I first arrived here,

00:31:39.540 --> 00:31:40.380 line:80%
my childhood friend

00:31:40.380 --> 00:31:41.220 line:80%
gave me a sachet

00:31:41.420 --> 00:31:43.220 line:80%
to ward off poisonous insects and ants.

00:31:43.460 --> 00:31:45.060 line:80%
That is how I could come and go freely.

00:31:45.620 --> 00:31:47.220 line:80%
So, you are not a local?

00:31:47.220 --> 00:31:48.060 line:80%
No.

00:31:48.380 --> 00:31:50.420 line:80%
I came here 17 or 18 years ago.

00:31:51.140 --> 00:31:53.180 line:80%
Life in the Li Sect used to be good.

00:31:53.540 --> 00:31:55.460 line:80%
Everyone lived honestly and peacefully.

00:31:55.860 --> 00:31:57.900 line:80%
But lately, they somehow started

00:31:59.340 --> 00:32:01.380 line:80%
to seize able-bodied men
to repair Bliss Palace

00:32:01.980 --> 00:32:02.860 line:80%
or force hunters

00:32:02.860 --> 00:32:05.500 line:80%
to risk their lives
to gather Shanci Mushrooms.

00:32:06.620 --> 00:32:08.140 line:80%
They are all deadly jobs.

00:32:08.460 --> 00:32:09.900 line:80%
Shanci Mushrooms are toxic, right?

00:32:10.420 --> 00:32:11.260 line:80%
What are they for?

00:32:11.420 --> 00:32:12.260 line:80%
No idea.

00:32:13.020 --> 00:32:14.700 line:80%
I was in a hurry to deliver them,

00:32:14.980 --> 00:32:16.620 line:80%
so I risked going into the forest.

00:32:17.020 --> 00:32:18.700 line:80%
I never expected to run

00:32:19.980 --> 00:32:20.820 line:80%
into Black Slayers.

00:32:21.140 --> 00:32:21.980 line:80%
Youfu,

00:32:22.900 --> 00:32:24.260 line:80%
tell your guests to come out.

00:32:26.153 --> 00:32:27.666 line:80%
- Why bring outsiders here?
- Exactly.

00:32:28.520 --> 00:32:29.593 line:80%
He brought outsiders here.

00:32:29.740 --> 00:32:30.580 line:80%
Youfu,

00:32:31.060 --> 00:32:33.220 line:80%
you should know the village rules.

00:32:33.500 --> 00:32:34.940 line:80%
No outsiders.

00:32:35.980 --> 00:32:36.820 line:80%
Village Chief,

00:32:37.260 --> 00:32:39.700 line:80%
these two are my lifesavers.

00:32:39.860 --> 00:32:40.700 line:80%
This morning,

00:32:40.900 --> 00:32:42.580 line:80%
when I went into the forest,

00:32:42.580 --> 00:32:44.020 line:80%
I ran into Black Slayers.

00:32:44.420 --> 00:32:45.700 line:80%
If not for them,

00:32:45.900 --> 00:32:47.980 line:80%
I would have died.

00:32:47.991 --> 00:32:49.324 line:80%
- Black Slayers?
- Black Slayers.

00:32:49.620 --> 00:32:50.700 line:80%
Where are the Black Slayers?

00:32:51.300 --> 00:32:52.420 line:80%
We killed them all

00:32:52.420 --> 00:32:53.391 line:80%
by accident.

00:32:53.402 --> 00:32:54.750 line:80%
- You killed them?
- They're dead.

00:32:54.761 --> 00:32:56.042 line:80%
But Black Slayers are not ghosts.

00:32:56.280 --> 00:32:57.120 line:80%
They're humans.

00:32:57.140 --> 00:32:59.980 line:80%
Lately, many young men
have gone missing.

00:32:59.980 --> 00:33:01.740 line:80%
The Black Slayers took them.

00:33:02.140 --> 00:33:03.880 line:80%
For you two to be able to kill them,

00:33:03.880 --> 00:33:05.600 line:80%
(Village Chief, Gui)
your skills must be extraordinary.

00:33:05.740 --> 00:33:06.580 line:80%
Indeed.

00:33:06.860 --> 00:33:09.300 line:80%
May I ask which sect you belong to?

00:33:10.100 --> 00:33:11.660 line:80%
- Qingque...
- We're from Qingzhu Gang.

00:33:12.500 --> 00:33:13.433 line:80%
My name is Feng Xiaohan.

00:33:13.700 --> 00:33:14.760 line:80%
This is my senior brother,

00:33:15.060 --> 00:33:15.900 line:80%
Dai Qingyun.

00:33:16.460 --> 00:33:18.020 line:80%
What is Qingzhu Gang?

00:33:18.020 --> 00:33:19.108 line:80%
We are from the Qingzhu Gang

00:33:19.119 --> 00:33:22.119 line:80%
by the Canglang River
beneath Mount Wutong.

00:33:22.580 --> 00:33:23.540 line:80%
But our gang leader

00:33:23.551 --> 00:33:25.184 line:80%
died suddenly
after drinking fake liquor.

00:33:26.220 --> 00:33:27.500 line:80%
So Qingzhu Gang

00:33:27.780 --> 00:33:28.700 line:80%
fell apart.

00:33:29.380 --> 00:33:30.580 line:80%
We have

00:33:31.020 --> 00:33:32.060 line:80%
nowhere to go

00:33:32.580 --> 00:33:34.340 line:80%
nor food guaranteed.

00:33:34.860 --> 00:33:37.580 line:80%
We remembered that we have
an uncle in the Li Sect,

00:33:37.860 --> 00:33:39.180 line:80%
so we came to seek refuge.

00:33:39.660 --> 00:33:42.540 line:80%
You two helped us kill
the Black Slayers.

00:33:42.780 --> 00:33:44.860 line:80%
We should've shown hospitality,

00:33:45.180 --> 00:33:47.110 line:80%
but the village rules...

00:33:48.220 --> 00:33:49.060 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:33:49.580 --> 00:33:50.940 line:80%
We won't stay overnight.

00:33:51.500 --> 00:33:53.100 line:80%
Please tell us which way

00:33:53.380 --> 00:33:54.580 line:80%
leads to Qinglong Altar.

00:33:56.820 --> 00:33:58.020 line:80%
Qinglong Altar?

00:33:58.660 --> 00:34:00.660 line:80%
What about it?

00:34:06.460 --> 00:34:08.740 line:80%
(Peace and Plenty)

00:34:08.740 --> 00:34:09.580 line:80%
It's not far

00:34:10.140 --> 00:34:11.820 line:80%
from here.

00:34:11.820 --> 00:34:13.060 line:80%
But lately, that place

00:34:13.620 --> 00:34:14.460 line:80%
has been unsettled.

00:34:14.740 --> 00:34:16.580 line:80%
Are you two truly going?

00:34:17.220 --> 00:34:18.820 line:80%
We're already here, so we'll go.

00:34:19.780 --> 00:34:21.940 line:80%
Thanks for preparing so thoroughly.

00:34:22.340 --> 00:34:23.860 line:80%
Change into these clothes.

00:34:23.924 --> 00:34:25.073 line:80%
You are outsiders, after all.

00:34:25.140 --> 00:34:26.260 line:80%
Better not draw attention.

00:34:27.100 --> 00:34:28.220 line:80%
This fabric

00:34:28.720 --> 00:34:30.020 line:80%
does not look like village cloth.

00:34:30.140 --> 00:34:31.060 line:80%
Where did it come from?

00:34:31.083 --> 00:34:33.268 line:80%
It belongs to Xing,
our village chief's granddaughter.

00:34:33.279 --> 00:34:34.812 line:80%
She serves as a maid at Qinglong Altar.

00:34:34.900 --> 00:34:36.020 line:80%
She works for the Li Sect?

00:34:36.180 --> 00:34:38.340 line:80%
Yes. Many of our villagers do.

00:34:38.440 --> 00:34:40.142 line:80%
They receive monthly wages,
rain or shine.

00:34:40.180 --> 00:34:41.766 line:80%
Far better than hunting or farming.

00:34:42.060 --> 00:34:42.900 line:80%
However,

00:34:43.100 --> 00:34:45.020 line:80%
there's been no news from some servants

00:34:45.031 --> 00:34:46.057 line:80%
working at Qinglong Altar,

00:34:46.380 --> 00:34:48.060 line:80%
and Xing hasn't returned
for a long time.

00:34:48.480 --> 00:34:49.380 line:80%
Miss Feng,

00:34:49.380 --> 00:34:50.220 line:80%
Mr. Dai,

00:34:50.380 --> 00:34:51.660 line:80%
is the person you are looking for

00:34:52.180 --> 00:34:53.300 line:80%
truly at Qinglong Altar?

00:34:54.180 --> 00:34:55.300 line:80%
He must be there.

00:34:56.740 --> 00:35:01.940 line:80%
(Qinglong Altar)

00:35:08.740 --> 00:35:09.700 line:80%
Perhaps

00:35:11.660 --> 00:35:12.780 line:80%
she is still on her way.

00:35:22.980 --> 00:35:24.340 line:80%
Go find your Xing.

00:35:28.420 --> 00:35:29.260 line:80%
Set off.

00:35:46.920 --> 00:35:57.580 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:36:16.340 --> 00:36:20.750 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:36:21.315 --> 00:36:25.930 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:36:26.270 --> 00:36:30.835 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:36:31.360 --> 00:36:35.660 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:36:38.605 --> 00:36:43.305 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:36:43.830 --> 00:36:48.120 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:36:48.780 --> 00:36:52.810 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:36:53.125 --> 00:36:58.250 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:36:58.825 --> 00:37:03.635 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:37:03.850 --> 00:37:08.020 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:37:08.745 --> 00:37:12.680 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:37:13.180 --> 00:37:18.455 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:37:41.185 --> 00:37:46.315 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:37:46.680 --> 00:37:51.050 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:37:51.315 --> 00:37:55.445 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:37:55.630 --> 00:38:01.205 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪